PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Energy, Mines and Resources of William (Steve) Vaughan, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Atomic Energy of Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Lois DeGroot, whose term has expired.
